tentang membahas penjualan buku saya.

00:21:39.186 --> 00:21:44.616
Atau apakah kami mencoba berbasa-basi
sambil menunggu editor bintang Anda?

00:21:46.600 --> 00:21:48.765
Di mana editor bintang Anda?

00:21:49.893 --> 00:21:50.735
Maaf.

00:22:05.215 --> 00:22:07.055
Maya, aku minta maaf.

00:22:07.324 --> 00:22:09.573
Aku mengalami masalah
di tempat parkir, dan...

00:22:12.694 --> 00:22:13.395
Itulah mengapa.

00:22:13.475 --> 00:22:15.738
Dan ditambah lalu lintas, lho.

00:22:16.092 --> 00:22:17.485
Aku sangat menyesal.

00:22:17.943 --> 00:22:19.344
Aku sungguh minta maaf.

00:22:42.748 --> 00:22:45.533
Abimanyu, temui Asmita Roy.

00:22:46.260 --> 00:22:48.586
Editor yang tadi kuceritakan padamu.

00:22:49.815 --> 00:22:55.055
