editor fiksi kami Shalini.

00:22:57.347 --> 00:23:00.435
Dan Asmita, ini Abimanyu Razdan.

00:23:02.986 --> 00:23:04.223
Raja romansa.

00:23:16.479 --> 00:23:17.378
Anda?

00:23:24.972 --> 00:23:26.923
Apakah kalian berdua saling kenal?

